{
  "texts": [
    "Comparison of the MultiSenseBadminton dataset [64] with existing public and non-public badminton datasets: In the \"Context\" column, \"C\" denotes collecting badminton data in a constrained, controlled environment, while \"F\" indicates data collection in the field during actual competitive play between two or more players.",
    "In the \"Task\" column, \"CLA.",
    "\", \"STAT. \"",
    "stands for action classification, action quality assessment, and cross-player statistical analysis.",
    "In the \"Target Population\" column, \"PR. \""
  ]
}